                          IMPORTANT NOTICE
================================================================================

This software is an ORIGINAL IMPLEMENTATION written from scratch by Lux
Industries Inc. It is NOT derived from any third-party FHE library including
but not limited to Zama, OpenFHE, SEAL, HElib, or any other implementation.

Our implementation is based solely on published academic research:
- Chillotti et al. "TFHE: Fast Fully Homomorphic Encryption Over the Torus"
  (Journal of Cryptology, 2020)
- Ducas & Micciancio "FHEW: Bootstrapping Homomorphic Encryption in Less
  Than a Second" (EUROCRYPT 2015)

Key innovations protected by our patent portfolio include:
- Pure Go TFHE Implementation Without CGO Dependencies
- Deterministic FHE Random Number Generation for Blockchain Consensus
- Transaction-Batch Amortized Bootstrapping for Block-Level Optimization
- Lazy Carry Propagation with Deterministic Noise Tracking
- Batch DAG Execution for FHE Operations with GPU Acceleration
- Precompile Gas Metering for Variable-Cost FHE Operations

